---
title: Mushroom & Veggie Noodles with Asparagus, Sesame Seeds & Crispy Shallots
description: Load your bowl with tender udon noodles plus a medley of colourful veggies. With our plant-based stir-fry
sauce to bring the whole meal together, this feast will have you throwing away the takeaway menu!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
